title: Amy Sees A Celebrity During Her ‘Staycation’ + Bobby’s Embarrassing Airport Accident + Lunchbox Lied to Get On Jerry Springer
itunes:title: Amy Sees A Celebrity During Her ‘Staycation’ + Bobby’s Embarrassing Airport Accident + Lunchbox Lied to Get On Jerry Springer
description:
Amy goes on a staycation with her family and runs into a celebrity at the bottom of one of the water slides. Bobby admits an embarrassing accident he had at the airport when traveling home over the weekend. Plus, Bobby talks about how Jerry Springer producers admitted the show was fake so we talk about how Lunchbox was on the show back in the day…and lied to get on!
